WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:18.071 --> 00:00:19.239
Sissy?

00:00:51.138 --> 00:00:52.338
Sissy.

00:00:54.508 --> 00:00:57.443
Get out of here, bud.
I mean it.

00:00:57.511 --> 00:00:59.111
I got to talk to you.

00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:01.080
Wes is in gilley's,
and we're leaving.

00:01:01.282 --> 00:01:02.515
I know you're leaving.

00:01:02.583 --> 00:01:05.518
I just want
to tell you something.

00:01:07.154 --> 00:01:09.455
I'm hard-headed,
and I'm prideful,

00:01:09.523 --> 00:01:10.956
And I want
to apologize

00:01:11.024 --> 00:01:14.460
Clear back to when I
hit you the first time.

00:01:18.198 --> 00:01:19.632
I love you, sissy.

00:01:26.774 --> 00:01:28.808
I love you, too, bud.

00:01:30.411 --> 00:01:31.511
You do?

00:01:31.578 --> 00:01:32.712
Mmm.

00:01:32.780 --> 00:01:36.616
I didn't know you came
to the trailer that day.

00:01:36.684 --> 00:01:39.619
If--if I'd known that,
I'd have called you.

00:01:39.687 --> 00:01:42.121
But she tore up
that note.

00:01:42.189 --> 00:01:44.791
You can ride
that goddamn bull--

00:01:44.858 --> 00:01:47.293
I don't want to ride it.

00:01:47.361 --> 00:01:48.795
And look,
screw mexico,

00:01:48.862 --> 00:01:52.097
Because we can do
anything we want--

00:01:52.333 --> 00:01:53.566
What happened
to your face?

00:01:53.867 --> 00:01:55.067
I got hit.

00:01:55.135 --> 00:01:57.603
Did he hit you?

00:01:57.671 --> 00:01:59.806
Goddamn, I'm gonna kill
that son of a bitch.

